author: jdcasey
msg: Changing the location of the Artifact-cloning method from org.apache.maven.artifact.factory.ArtifactFactory.cloneArtifact(..) to org.apache.maven.artifact.ArtifactUtils.copyArtifact(..), which is now a static method. This separates the copy method from a specific artifact implementation, while at the same time avoiding embedding of this method in a component instance.
